<dd> <b>Monotone piecewise cubic interpolation</b>.
     SIAM J. Numerc. Anal., Vol. 17, No. 2, April 1980, pp. 238-246</dd>
</dl>
</html>",
        revisions="<html>
<ul>
<li><i>Nov., 2005</i>
    by <a href=\"mailto:Martin.Otter@DLR.de\">Martin Otter</a>:<br>
    Designed and implementated.</li>
</ul>
</html>"));
end regRoot2;
